{"word":"G3820 - παλαιός - palaiós - pal-ah-yos' - Old","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παλαιός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">palaiós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pal-ah-yos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Old</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பழைய - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. old, ancient"},{"paragraph":"2. no longer new, worn by use, the worse for wear, old"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3819 - πάλαι - pálai - pal'-ahee/3819\">G3819</a>; <i>antique</i>, that is, <i>not recent</i>, <i>worn out:</i> - old.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G3819/3819\">G3819</a>, <a href=\"#/G3820/3820\">G3820</a>, <a href=\"#/G3821/3821\">G3821</a>, <a href=\"#/G3822/3822\">G3822</a>"}]}